           Jamestown: Legend Of The Lost Colony is a neo-classical top-down
           shooter for up to 4 players, set on 17th-century British Colonial
           Mars. It features all the intensity, depth, and lovingly handcrafted
           pixels of a classic arcade shooter, with a modern twist: deeply-
           integrated cooperative gameplay.
           Unlike most top-down shooters, which give multiple players a shared
           pool of lives or continues, Jamestown does something different. So
           long as any player survives, the team can be brought back from death.
           By giving every player the power to rescue their team from the jaws
           of destruction, Jamestown creates an exhilarating cooperative expe-
           rience where everyone's contribution truly matters. Win or lose, your
           team will do it together.
